		<description>
			This is a flexible TableView specialized in settings for Android / iOS.
			There are various cells such as (EntryCell, LabelCell, ButtonCell, CommandCell, SwitchCell, CheckboxCell, RadioCell, PickerCell, TextPickerCell, NumberPickerCell, TimePickerCell, DatePickerCell)
		</description>
		<releaseNotes>
			Complete revamp of API and structure.

			All supported cells now align correctly.

			Some event handlers added, with more coming.
			Removed unnecessary code and attributes for all cells.

			Popup Cells ( PickerCell, TextPickerCell, NumberPickerCell, TimePickerCell, DatePickerCell ) support styling for the popups where applicable and value change event added.

			Accessory Cells ( SwitchCell, CheckboxCell, RadioCell ) value change event added.

			Checkable Cells ( SwitchCell, CheckboxCell ) now use a single consolidated Checked attribute. Previously it was On and Checked. Also, value change event added.

			EntryCell has a value change event added.

			Command Cells ( ButtonCell, CommandCell ) now support short and long press clicks. 
			
			ButtonCell is now a native Button on each platform, instead of a clone of the CommandCell.

			And lastly, now uses AndroidX libraries natively.
		</releaseNotes>
